[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    135[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    136[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Fix:** Expand the VPC endpoint list: "VPC endpoints required: S3 (Gateway), CloudWatch Logs (Interface), SageMaker API (Interface), SageMaker Runtime (Interface), Step Functions (Interface), Glue (Interface), Redshift (Interface or use Redshift in the same VPC), KMS (Interface). Lambda functions that call AWS services from within the VPC require these endpoints or a NAT Gateway."
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    137[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
